channel.title: For anyone interested in making fast GPs
channel.description:
Basically all I need is a person (being a member on runescape) who has at least started the "Recipe for Disaster" quest, basically as to those who the above apply may know grapes cost 1 gp each from the buy food option on the "Culinomancer Chest" I am paying 10-20 gp per grape people get by world hopping (pricing varies depending on amount which you sell). And Theres virtually no limit to the amount which I would buy... (I need quite alot of them).
TYVM in advance - anyone who may be interested contact me by any means that you know how: l3eta
